'''Abyssin''' was the official [[Language/Legends|language]] of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Byss (Abyssin)/Legends|Byss]], home of the [[Abyssin/Legends|Abyssin]] [[Species/Legends|species]]. Abyssin had both a spoken and written form. The spoken form used mainly growls and grunts that many species considered primitive-sounding. The [[Abyssin (written language)|written form]] of language used only a small number of simple [[Hieroglyphics|hieroglyphs]].<ref name="Ultimate Alien Anthology" />

